Package com.dsi.ant.chip

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAntChip
    This is the interface to an ANT Chip, which is an abstracted piece of ANT hardware.
    IAntChipDetector
    Specifies the interface the ANT Radio Service uses to communicate with a remote service providing a transport to ANT hardware.
    IAntChipDetectorEventReceiver
    Updates for known ANT chips
    IAntChipEventReceiver
    Updates from the ANT hardware
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AntChipBase
    Extended by a hardware specific ANT chip implementation.
    AntChipDetectorBase
    Extended by a hardware specific ANT chip detector implementation.
    AntChipState
    This class contains constants representing the various states an ANT chip can be in.
    ChipProviderMetaData
    Defines the values that will match the meta-data information defined in the Android Manifest of any ANT Chip Provider Service.
